cdata.name: ZestCoin
cdata.desc:
Zestcoin is PoW cryptocurrency based on the Quark algorithm. It features a second-layer network of masternodes that process near instant and private transactions. ZEST's block reward system sees 80% of its reward allocated to to Masternodes, 15% to coin-holders and 5% to The Zest Foundation.

Click here for Masternode stats from masternodes.online.
